```
# Google Apps Script specific ignores
**/.clasp.json
**/.gs.cache.json
**/dist/

# Compiled JavaScript (if any)
*.js.map
*.min.js

# Logs and temporary files
*.log
*.tmp
*.temp

# Environment variables
.env
.env.local
*.env.*

# Editors
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# OS generated files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Coverage reports
coverage/
htmlcov/
*.coverage

# Distribution artifacts
dist/
build/
```